===Etymology===
Named after [[botanist]] [[w:Robert Brown (botanist)|Robert Brown]] (1773-1858) who investigated the movement of [[pollen]] suspended in [[water]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}
# [[random|Random]] [[motion]] of [[particle]]s suspended in a [[fluid]], arising from those particles being struck by individual [[molecule]]s of the fluid.

====Synonyms====
*[[Brownian movement]]

